data.description:
Come and see this rare Dutch Colonial style home overlooking Swan Lake in Midtown Tulsa. Spend your time walking around the neighborhood lake.  Enjoy the nearby shops and restaurants of Utica Square and Cherry Street.  Local hospitals are just around the corner.  Classic floor plan: Living spaces downstairs, bedrooms and bath upstairs. Gas log fireplace. Enjoy your morning coffee in the sun room beside the living room.  Formal dining. Kitchen features the refrigerator, antique styled range/oven, dishwasher, and disposal. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms and 1 full classic bath. Primary bedroom includes a gas insert fireplace and private deck with ground level access. Front yard overlooks the nature filled lake. Private gated drive,  2 vehicle carport with additional 3 car parking. Basement features a private 1 bed/bath apartment with access to washer/dryer in basement. 
There is an additional separate 1bed, 1bath apartment with private w/d connections in the back yard as well! With your personal touch this would be a Swan Lake Jewel!
